{"title":"山雪","authors":["聪聪"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":3,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聪聪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山，是雪的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最喜爱的摇篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当梯田不再荒芜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再贫寒……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪，是山的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的打扮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当梯田返老还童"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"焕发出新颜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈！看如今，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啥能比雪美呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它能化为金谷、银棉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让亩产翻番！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪在山的怀里笑了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山在雪的歌里狂欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，山是雪的摇篮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪是山的衣衫。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}